<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.4">
<l>antaṇaṉait tañcameṉ ṟāṭpaṭṭār āḻāmē</l>
<l>vantaṇaintu kāttaḷikkum vallāḷaṉ - kontaṇainta</l>
<l>poṉkaṇṭāṟ pūṇātē kōṇākam pūṇṭāṉē</l>
<l>yeṉkaṇṭāy neñcē yiṉi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that those, who serve the brahmin as refuge, will not sink</l>
<l>the strong man comes close [and] provides protection, the one who,</l>
<l>if he sees gold that approaches a cluster, does not put it on [but] puts snakes on,</l>
<l>– what [of it], look now, heart?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
